1.[… … and whosoever trades]
2.[wholesale that merchandise which they]
3.[buy in Shammar must] 
4.[buy it within] 
5.[(the confederation of) Qatabān, one man]
6.[from another; so too] 
7.[whoever trades in any]
8.[merchandise in Shammar] 
9.[by night and]
10.[equally by morning. And] 
11.[the king of Qatabān himself]
12.[exercises authority over all]
13.[commerce and goods]
14.[that enter his territory. And] 
15.[no king shall remove]
16.[this decree.]</tei:ab>
